Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.55,0:33:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing at all.\NEventually
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.55,0:33:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,uh you pretty much transcend any\Ninterest in the body and where it is is
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.15,0:33:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,not of any particular interest.\NAnd eventually the dimension you reach a
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.48,0:33:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,state which I have tried to explain\Nbefore
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.84,0:33:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,because I feel responsible for your\Nknowingness of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.96,0:34:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There there is a state beyond beyond all\Nthe prior states.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.96,0:34:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,um a state of pure austerity.\NIt is like the closest thing I can say
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.67,0:34:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,it's like a very high pass.\NI've spoken of it before as the high
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.28,0:34:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,past because the members of this\Naudience will be going to those states.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.67,0:34:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you're in this class. These\Nare all the Buddhas coming and that's
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.32,0:34:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,why you're here. Why else would anybody\Nbe here? So
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.52,0:34:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,all the great teachers of the future are\Nhere
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.52,0:34:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,are already here in this room.\NThat is so Lord resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.15,0:34:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,All the great teachers of the future are\Nalready here.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.56,0:34:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So you accept that responsibility\Nby being here. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.72,0:35:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,that you will each and every one of you\Nbecome the great teachers of the future
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.59,0:35:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,if and some of you even in this\Nlifetime. So
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.24,0:35:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,when you surrendered everything to God\Nthrough meditation and completion and
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.07,0:35:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,letting go all attachments and aversions\None reaches a very high plane
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.88,0:35:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,where no one exists. No one there's\Nnobody there.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.00,0:35:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This high pass\NUh
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.48,0:35:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,you can see you can you can see who's\Nbeen there and I as I've said before I
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.11,0:35:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,saw those who had been there\Nand at that level comes the great
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.04,0:35:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,temptation which I've described as the\Nessence of the luciferic.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.00,0:35:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you know you are beyond all\Nconsequences. Now that you know you
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.35,0:36:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,karma no longer applies to you.\NAll power is yours. Use it. The
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.32,0:36:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,temptation then is to utilize\Nthis infinite power which is now yours
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.72,0:36:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,for personal you might say\Nfor
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.24,0:36:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,power over others\Nbecause now you you have the power to
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.07,0:36:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,actually take power over domains.\NYou actually have power over domains.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.56,0:36:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You've traversed all these domains where\Nthe lower levels of consciousness and
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.88,0:36:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,mere mortals have gotten tripped up. And\Nnow you are in a rarified rarified
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.24,0:36:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,place.\NAll power is yours. You're beyond the
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.35,0:36:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,consequences of karma.\NAnd the temptation is power for its own
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.88,0:36:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,sake.\NPower for its own sake. Not because of
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.28,0:36:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,some gain of the power. power for its\Nown sake. And this I call the luciferic
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.52,0:37:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,temptation.\NThe luciferic temptation is power for
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.32,0:37:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,its own sake. The satanic temptation is\Nwickedness. And people in this group
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.56,0:37:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,won't have any trouble with getting, you\Nknow, refuting w uh letting go the
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.72,0:37:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,attractions of wickedness.\NUh but but the power overall because you
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.59,0:37:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,could fall for the illusion that well\Nyou'll only use the power for good. You
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.52,0:37:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,mean good as you see it, right?\NSo it is the ultimate luciferic
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.92,0:37:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,temptation.\NThere is nothing there except the silent
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.24,0:37:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,knowingness.\NAll power is yours. Own it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.59,0:37:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And I saw that the Lord Jesus Christ\Nwent through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.72,0:37:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw those who went through that high\Npass. Very few in number. But anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.16,0:37:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,what was I going to tell you about the\Npass? Oh yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.92,0:38:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh\Nand then to to go through the next door
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.52,0:38:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,to go through the next door\Nyou realize that you have surrendered
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.32,0:38:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,everything. everything,\Nincluding even the desire for power over
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.11,0:38:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,others.\NAnd then it dawns on you that the one
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.04,0:38:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,thing you still have\Nor the illusion, the belief system you
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.59,0:38:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,have, you've let go all attachments and\Nand aversions, attachments and aversions
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.48,0:38:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,is your attachment to life.\NUh oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.56,0:38:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You've let go the attachment to the\Ndetails of life. Carninal and money and
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.20,0:38:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,power and prestige and excitement and\Nthrills and spills. Space diving. All of
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.28,0:38:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,it.\NCanoeing.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.59,0:39:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,All the great temptations. Pizza.\NPizza. Cheeseburgers. You all go.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.24,0:39:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,There is nothing left in this high pass\Nexcept your own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.07,0:39:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And you will remember this in this high\Npass. There is nothing left but your
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.88,0:39:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,identification that you are that which\Nlife is. That you are life. That that
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.59,0:39:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,your life radiates forth from your\Nreality.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.68,0:39:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You've laid everything down at the feet\Nof God. everything. You've let
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.48,0:39:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,everything this world cherishes.\NYou've surrendered it all to God through
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.64,0:39:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,the pathway of negation. Not this, not\Nthat. Not money, not riches, not looks,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.04,0:39:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,not fame, not fortune.\NYou've got nothing left. You've given it
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.11,0:39:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,all away. Surrendered it all. No\Nattachments, no virgins.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.72,0:40:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, what have you got left to\Nsurrender to God?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.40,0:40:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,your life.\NYou have to surrender your life to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.48,0:40:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is the high pass beyond all\Nhigh passes. We have permission to
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.20,0:40:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrate the high pass. It's over 900,\N930, 925, 930 at about level 925.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.28,0:40:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,uh\Nsome of you will be reaching that
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.92,0:40:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,otherwise you wouldn't be in this class\Nor else would you be in a class on how
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.52,0:40:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,to transcend\Nand 25 to a thousand unless you were
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.76,0:40:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,destined for that you understand you're\Nlistening to your own destiny so in that
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.32,0:41:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,life then you realize I have nothing\Nleft oh god
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.80,0:41:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Except my life itself. I surrender my\Nlife to thee, oh Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.11,0:41:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And with that there's a terrible fear of\Ndying.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.72,0:41:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,There is an agony of dying.\NWhen you experience the agony of dying,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.64,0:41:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,you know you're in the right place.\NThis is the agony that you agreed to go
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.00,0:41:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,through to get to the other side.\Nthat which you have believed throughout
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.76,0:41:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,all these lifetimes, all the way back to\Neternity practically
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.04,0:41:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,down to the level of the bacteria. All\Nthrough the evolution of life, all
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.56,0:41:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,through the evolution of consciousness,\Nthat which you have believed is the very
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.76,0:42:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,core and source of your existence, you\Nare now asked to surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.88,0:42:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the fear of non-existence comes up\Nagain now in a different level. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.07,0:42:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Now comes the knowingness.\NNow comes the knowingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.16,0:42:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's safe to lay down your life to God\Nbecause all fear is illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.59,0:42:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the knowingness that came out\Nof I don't know how many lifetimes ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.92,0:42:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,nine, 10 lifetimes ago. All fear is\Nillusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.88,0:42:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So out of nowhere because there's nobody\Nup there with you in this space. There's
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.11,0:42:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,no otherness.\NThere is only the infinite knowingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.68,0:42:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The infinite knowingness has to come\Nthrough with an absolute certainty of
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.92,0:42:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,those who have walked through the past.\NUhhuh.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.68,0:43:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,All fear is illusion. And so you lay\Ndown your life and surrender it and give
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.07,0:43:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,it to God.\NAnd then
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.48,0:43:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and then\Nthe splendor of divinity
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.11,0:43:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,shines forth\Nas the as all that exists now or ever
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.04,0:43:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,more.\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.00,0:43:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permission to calibrate that. Oh\NLord, that opening beyond the door
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.35,0:43:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrates at 1,00 is just that is the\Ndoorway to 1,000 to the knowingness of
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.16,0:43:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,divinity.\NAha.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.07,0:43:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You thereby have owned\Nyour own divinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.24,0:43:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You own your own divinity and you stop\Ndenying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.76,0:44:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And now you the self with the smallest S\Nhas become truly the self with a capital
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.59,0:44:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,S.\NThe surrender is beyond recall.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.11,0:44:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Once having surrendered your life,\Nyou cannot recall it. Now you have no
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.83,0:44:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,control over your life from that point\Non.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.68,0:44:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh dear.\NNow, what'll I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.80,0:44:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear.\NWhat do you do then? Oh, well, you
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.31,0:44:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,teach. Oh, I didn't even know what it\Nwas.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.83,0:44:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess if you're willing to do so, and\NI think it was by karmic agreement that
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.68,0:45:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I agreed to do so,\Nthen you serve
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.28,0:45:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,God. You by serving your fellow man\Nby loving and serving your fellow man,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.52,0:45:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,you serve God. They're not different.\NThey are not God or your fellow man.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.56,0:45:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,They are God as your fellow man.\NOh god. What more could you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.28,0:45:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Finding out that all cheeseburgers are\NGod. Oh boy. I thought I had to give up
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.68,0:45:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,cheeseburgers to find God. And you find\Nthat cheeseburgers are God.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.64,0:45:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Infinite\Ndivinity expressing itself as a
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.16,0:45:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,cheeseburger.\NThe more you love God, the more you love
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.35,0:46:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,a cheeseburger.\Nthe higher states take you through and
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.16,0:46:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,we've mentioned some of them\Nuh joy, bliss,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.00,0:46:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,uh ecstasy.\NMany of those states I went through here
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.59,0:46:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,at the chapel of the Holy Cross. When I\Ncame back out here many decades ago, the
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.56,0:46:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Chapel of the Holy Cross was open all\Nnight. The visitors were all gone by
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.11,0:46:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,5:00.\NPopulation of this town was only, I
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.00,0:46:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,don't know, 850 or something. Anyway, by\N5:00, all the the visitors had gone
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.40,0:46:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and you had the chapel of the Holy Cross\Ncompletely to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.96,0:46:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,In those days they left the candles\Nburning all night and they left the
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.44,0:46:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,beautiful music playing all night. So\Nthere you had the chapel of the Holy
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.44,0:46:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Cross all to yourself all night long.\NYou could meditate
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.64,0:47:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and uh read states of extreme ecstasy.\NI found out that you have to let go the
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.83,0:47:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,ecstasy also\Nthat beyond ecstasy. I thought this this
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.44,0:47:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,oh lord I can't lay down. The joy was so\Nphenomenal as a Rama Krishna ex
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.16,0:47:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,experience it the ecstatic joy\Nthe presence of God is infinite joy
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.92,0:47:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,is ecstatic ecstasy beyond any ecstasy\Nthat one experiences in the ordinary
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.96,0:47:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,human domain. This is ecstasy.\NEcstasy on the level of a universe like
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.56,0:47:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,a universe of ecstasy.\NThis too you have to surrender and
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.00,0:47:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,beyond the ecstasy\Nlay the infinite peace. So I remember
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.64,0:48:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,surrendering kneeling at the older\Nand then the ecstasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.92,0:48:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,at the feet of the Lord. Yeah.\NAnd then came the infinite peace beyond
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.16,0:48:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,which there is no understanding. Yes.\NRight.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.20,0:48:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to make sure that that\Nknowingness is imprinted for the day
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.88,0:48:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,that it will be recalled\Nbecause I've known all along these are
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.92,0:48:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,the Buddhas of the future.\NThese are the great teachers here now
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.48,0:48:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,present.\NWhy else would you be here? This is not
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.59,0:48:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,a course on tennis.\NIf you're going to be great tennis
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.64,0:48:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,players, I would be a great tennis\Ncoach.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.20,0:48:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not on tennis. Therefore, everyone\Nhere is profoundly spiritually committed
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.20,0:48:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,u now and for the future. So, it must\Nhave been something you said. Well, you
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.72,0:48:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,can always change your mind later and\Nsay,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.52,0:49:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'll go back to booze and gambling and\Nwomen, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.72,0:49:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,except you won't be you you can't go\Nback. It's not possible to go back
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.04,0:49:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,because now you know better. Once you've\Nexperienced higher celestial realms,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.40,0:49:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,you won't settle for less anymore. You\Nwon't settle for less. Uh only the most
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.24,0:49:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,ecstatic. All right. So we'll go to the\Nnext uh next.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.44,0:49:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So that should handle union mystica. The\Necstasies uh joys and
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.04,0:49:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,difficulties of the great Christian\Nmystics are written uh in the literature
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.64,0:49:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and their stories are indeed heartening.\NAnd when that state of profound love
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.07,0:49:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,comes and disappears, you feel like God\Nhas deserted you. Oh, where hast thou
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.52,0:49:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,gone, my love? Where hast thou gone?\NAnd um
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.88,0:50:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,recent saint who died recently uh wrote\Nof that
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.76,0:50:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,um Mother Teresa. Yes. Uh went into high\Nstates and then wondered where has where
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.72,0:50:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,has divinity gone? Yes.\Nexpecting however divinity to take the
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.96,0:50:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,form of Jesus Christ which I thought was\Nwhat her difficulty was because it
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.83,0:50:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't necessarily take the form of a\Nfigure much less a divine figure in the
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.68,0:50:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,high past there was no form there there\Nwas no personage no entity
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.04,0:50:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing with the name nothing came out\Nof the clouds and said I am God I'm
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.35,0:50:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesus I am Buddha\NThe knowingness was nonlinear,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.72,0:50:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,all prevailing, all pervasive, all\Ninclusive.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.59,0:50:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Because if you were waiting for the\Npersonage of Jesus, that would leave out
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.35,0:51:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,all that is not Jesus, would it not? No.\NThe presence of divinity is allness, not
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.20,0:51:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,a personality as such. So that was uh\Nunderstandable.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.64,0:51:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So you've let go of identifying yourself\Nas
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.64,0:51:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the physicality or its senses,\Nmuch less delineations, sex, age, that
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.76,0:51:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,you're part of the animal kingdom. You\Nlet go of identifying yourself as your
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.48,0:51:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,history. I was born so and so and I had\Nthese and that other experiences
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.76,0:51:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and oh I remember that and I can recall\Nthat. So now you think you are this
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.00,0:51:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the physicality born such and such\Na place and it went through all these
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.24,0:51:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,various\Nexperiences which and and emotions and
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.16,0:51:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,feelings\Nand it ends up with desires and
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.68,0:51:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,aversions.\NSo the pathway, the direct pathway is to
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.72,0:52:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,let go of all attractions, all desires,\Nall wants and all negations. Neither
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.52,0:52:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,negation nor attraction.\NYou give up seeing yourself as the
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.52,0:52:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,decider, the chooser, the source of\Nvalition. You give up the naivity that
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.11,0:52:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,you are the cause of anything.\NYou're not the cause of anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.16,0:52:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The infinite power of consciousness is\Nso profound to think that little puny
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.00,0:52:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,you could decide be the decider of\Nanything is a great pomposity.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.28,0:52:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The poopy little ego that doesn't have\Nas much power as my little finger can
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.64,0:52:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,hardly be the great decider of all your\Nlife decisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.72,0:52:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Now something very very profound is\Nmaking the decisions and it's not your
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.52,0:52:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,personal self at all. So you begin to\Nsee that when you let go of the
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.40,0:53:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,pomposity and grandiosity that there is\Na personal you that is making choices
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.31,0:53:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and decisions\Nthat such an entity would be talking
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.80,0:53:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,right now and if he did I want anything\Nto do with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.88,0:53:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What do I want with anybody that talks\Nthis way?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.48,0:53:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,some kind of a nut job, wouldn't you\Nsay?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.40,0:53:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you can't be the doer or you'd be an\Nidiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.31,0:53:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither can you be recipient.\NSo, in the high high places, there is no
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.35,0:53:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,other. There is not an other. There is\Nno archangel talking to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.24,0:53:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no spirit guide talking to you.\NThere's nothing floating around with
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.11,0:53:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,wings speaking to you.\NThere is no other. And as much as you
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.31,0:53:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,are all that is, how could there be an\Nother?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.92,0:53:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Great spiritual error.\NOne of very famous religion came out of
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.48,0:53:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,believing that some archangel was the\Nsource of the the knowingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.28,0:54:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NThat which you are eventually becomes
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.07,0:54:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,the teacher, the knower is all in the\None. And there is no doingness involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.44,0:54:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If you uh if your reality of the self is\Nall that there is, all that there is,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.96,0:54:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,how could there be an other o e? What\Nwould the other be? It would have to be
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.11,0:54:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,not self with a capital S. Therefore, it\Ncould hardly be divinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.44,0:54:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,People who get their spiritual\Ninstructions from otherness are prone to
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.92,0:54:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,fallacy. And very often before too many\Nyears when you calibrate them early and
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.24,0:54:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,you calibrate them later you see they\Nfail drastically because how can there
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.31,0:54:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,be some other entity?\NThe other entity is hardly going to be
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.31,0:54:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,an angelic or divine one. Could they be?\NWhy would some other entity
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.11,0:55:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,want to interfere with your becoming a\NBuddha unless its intention was to make
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.55,0:55:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,sure you don't become a Buddha because\Nthe Buddha does not take instructions
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.28,0:55:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,from some other in Buddha land.\NThere is no other. By definition, the
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.07,0:55:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Buddha nature is complete and total\Nallness. So how could there be some
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.40,0:55:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,other?\NI'm the Buddha of allness and now some
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.40,0:55:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,other voice comes out of the\Nethers
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.72,0:55:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,dictating things to me. You see the self\Nthe negation the absurdity of such a
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.64,0:55:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,claim. Yes. So the teachers who get\Ntheir instructions from others are
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.48,0:55:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,somewhere along the line. I'm not saying\Nthe bad but they are not the ultimate
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.00,0:55:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,state of of teacher.\NAll right? So you give up the illusion
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.79,0:55:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,that you are the the doer, you're the\Nwinner, you're the loser, or that there
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.92,0:56:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,is anything to get. There is nothing to\Nget.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.96,0:56:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,There is only the realization of the\Ntruth of what you are. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.35,0:56:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to get.\NEven to get that truth is is to lose
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.59,0:56:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,because that would be a belief system.\NYou have to let go all belief systems.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.04,0:56:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget about the Buddha nature,\Nall that hulum,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.24,0:56:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesus nature, Buddha nature,\NMohab nature, whatever nature you want
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.07,0:56:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,to call it.\NBut the minute you give it a name, you
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.00,0:56:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,give it a limitation. The minute it's\Neliminated, the minute you have a
