Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.72,0:57:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Here on the Buddha road telling me\Nyou're a Buddha.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.44,0:57:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Doom. Doom cuffs. Doomcuff.\NYou're not the doer. You don't not
