Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.00,0:59:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah. Yes.\NThere's no end to Looneyville, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.79,0:59:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NYou you give up intellection, education.
