Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.07,0:59:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,At that point, fear arises that you're\Nlost.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.68,1:00:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The best thing to do there is to rejoice\Nthat you are lost.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.00,1:00:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh God, I am lost. I don't know where\NI'm in time, space. I've forgotten my
